<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="45">[Lesotho] Basutoland. Above the Sani Pass, among stones, 9800 ft [2987 m alt.], 3 Feb 1959, M. McCallum Webster 483b (holotype: K (K000345250 [image!])).</paragraph>
